<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Unsupported on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/unsupported/</link><description>Recent content in Unsupported on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/unsupported/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Scala UnsupportedOperationException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/scala-unsupportedoperation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/scala-unsupportedoperation/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;UnsupportedOperationException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when attempting an operation on a collection or object that does not support it. This commonly happens when trying to modify an immutable collection or calling a method not implemented by the concrete class.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling &lt;code&gt;add&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;remove&lt;/code&gt; on an immutable collection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using mutable methods on Java &lt;code&gt;unmodifiable&lt;/code&gt; collections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attempting unsupported operation on empty collection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling abstract method without implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use mutable collections for modification:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>NotSupportedException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/not-supported/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/not-supported/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NotSupportedException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when an operation is attempted that is not supported by the object or implementation. This is common with read-only collections, abstract types, or platform-specific operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modifying read-only collections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling abstract methods without implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Platform-specific operations on wrong platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unsupported encoding or format&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Modifying read-only collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; readOnly &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[|&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|].&lt;/span&gt;AsReadOnly()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;readOnly&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;0&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; 10 &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NotSupportedException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Work with mutable collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; mutable arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[|&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;0&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; 10 &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// works
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Using unsupported method
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; bytes &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; System.Text.Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; decoded &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; System.Text.Encoding.ASCII.GetString&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// may lose data
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use supported encoding
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; decoded &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; System.Text.Encoding.UTF8.GetString&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: ReadOnly collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; List.toSeq
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Array.ofSeq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;SetValue&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;10&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; 0&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// works, but:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; readOnly &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;AsReadOnly()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;readOnly&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;IsReadOnly &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// true, can&amp;#39;t modify
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Unimplemented method
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;AbstractClass&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;abstract&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;member&lt;/span&gt; Area&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;float&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Shape() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Can&amp;#39;t instantiate abstract class
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Platform not supported
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;System.Environment.OSVersion.Platform &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// may be PlatformID on wrong OS
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/invalid-operation5"&gt;InvalidOperationException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/argument-exception"&gt;ArgumentException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>UnsupportedOperationException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/unsupported-operation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/unsupported-operation/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;UnsupportedOperationException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you try to perform an operation that isn&amp;rsquo;t supported by the object. This is common with read-only collections, abstract types, or when calling methods on immutable structures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modifying immutable collections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling methods on abstract types&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unsupported operation for the collection type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Platform-specific operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Modifying immutable collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;list &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// UnsupportedOperationException (or compile error)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Create new collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; newList &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// List(1, 2, 3, 4)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Calling unsupported method
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; empty &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;head &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// UnsupportedOperationException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Pattern match or use headOption
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; empty &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; head &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;head&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Nil&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Empty list&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Or
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;headOption &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// None
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: head on empty list
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;head &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// UnsupportedOperationException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: tail on empty list
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;tail &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// UnsupportedOperationException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: readOnlyBuffer
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; buffer &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; scala&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;collection&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;mutable&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ListBuffer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; readOnly &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; buffer&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;toList
